# 🌟 Royal Trusts

**Royal Trusts** is a parent company that serves as the foundation for multiple ventures across various industries.  
It manages and develops firms in **technology**, **pre-production**, **post-production**, **film making**, and other **business ventures**, with the goal of expanding into new domains in the future.

---

## 🏗️ Project Overview

This website represents the official online presence of **Royal Trusts**, highlighting its purpose, upcoming ventures, and creative divisions.  
It serves as a central hub connecting all brands and companies under the Royal Trusts umbrella.

---

## 🛠️ Built With
- **HTML** — Structure and layout  
- **CSS** — Styling and responsive design  
- **JavaScript** — Interactive elements and animations  

